{"tid":2217056,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬道立被《大公報》《文匯報》開火批鬥","createTime":"2020-09-25T07:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T08:23:57.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"064154ef918ffd050c2541856760f7e536ef3c76","tid":2217056,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:22:21.000Z","msg":"馬道立聲明︱《大公》《文匯》發功再向馬官開火頭版批鬥<br />\n2小時前<br />\n<br />\n早前大肆批評司法機關的中共喉舌《大公報》和《文匯報》，今日在終院首席法官馬道立發聲明兩日後，以大篇幅向馬道立發動第二波攻勢。<strong>其中《大公》更以頭版大字標題質問馬道立：「馬官大人 你在迴避改革！」</strong>又以前終院常任法官列顯倫、前刑事檢控專員江樂士等人的言論批評馬道立聲明。<br />\n<br />\n《大公》今日以A1、A2兩版對馬道立口誅筆伐。當中列顯倫接受《大公》訪問時，沒有評論馬道立發聲明的目的，僅指馬道立聲明是要帶出「你要批評，要有事實才批評」的信息，認為市民單憑法庭判來批評會「好削、好弱」，應耐心旁聽案件整個聆訊，了解事實及和判決原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200925/LBY6BVXH75D4BKWRVMNZFT2QRY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200925%2FLBY6BVXH75D4BKWRVMNZFT2QRY%2F&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzsQbtkMcGro9tlpYeKwNq%2B0%3D&h=fe2ce481\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200925%2FLBY6BVXH75D4BKWRVMNZFT2QRY%2F&h=45bf7707\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200925/LBY6BVXH75D4BKWRVMNZFT2QRY/</a>"},{"pid":"f895364da8c40fc1aee150cfe6eb584bbd66810a","tid":2217056,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:22:57.000Z","msg":"昨日仲有人以為馬道立係幫港共辯護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8709b639c8b36ed0709b7e70235a75ddfb64d7","tid":2217056,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ed338255cb8f2c01f60db4ac1f7cf99bec67e9","tid":2217056,"uid":77625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:23:58.000Z","msg":"你在迴避改革<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile